constructor.details: Specify the OpenOraclePriceData address, addresses for approved off-chain and on-chain data providers.

params.data_: is the address for the OpenOraclePriceData contract
params.onChainSources_: is the list of authorized on-chain souces addresses
params.sources_: is the list of authorized addresses to provide/sign off-chain data

params._symbol: is the price symbol such as 'ETH/USD' etc...

params.sources_: The sources to use when calculating the median price
params.symbol: The symbol to calculate the median price of

medianPrice(string,address[]).return: median The median price over the set of sources

postPrices(bytes[],bytes[],string[]).details: We let anyone pay to post anything, but only sources count for prices.

params.messages: The messages to post to the oracle
params.signatures: The signatures for the corresponding messages

getPrice(string).notice: Allows users to get median price data

medianPrice(string,address[]).notice: Calculates the median price over any set of sources

postPrices(bytes[],bytes[],string[]).notice: Primary entry point to post and recalculate prices
